</emphasis>
</emphasis>
Metasoma 0.70 (0.68–0.76)× as long as wide; pilosity sparse, setae of medium length; 
<collectionCode box="[528,543,350,374]" name="Tavera, Department of Geology and Geophysics" pageId="69" pageNumber="881">T</collectionCode>
